  "description": "<p><u><strong>📣 URGENT! RETAIL ADMIN ASSISTANTS @ CENTRAL/NORTH | UP TO $2.2K </strong></u> </p><p>📍Location: Central/North regions  </p><p>💰Salary: $2,000-$2,200 </p><p>🗓️Working days: Mon-Fri </p><p>🕑Shift hours: 10.45am-8.30pm </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Perform store administrative functions, including documentation, data entry, and filing </p></li><li><p>Process SAP-related tasks such as invoice verification and goods receipt entries </p></li><li><p>Manage incoming phone calls and replenish office and housekeeping supplies </p></li><li><p>Assist with stocktaking and carried out additional duties as assigned by the Retail Manager </p></li></ul><p>Requirements:  </p><ul><li><p>2 years experience or more in retail/hospitality industry  </p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office </p></li><li><p>Able to work immediately/Has short notice </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
